# Arcade Adventure full auto script

This script will fully automatically play the adventure game for you.
It will start by farming 11 keys, so don't wonder if it apears to be stuck betwenn the starting room and the first room. 
After it got the keys it will start to clear the rooms always aiming for the highest difficulty it can savely defeat. Farming keys inbetween whenever necessary. 


To Start the script press the R key. 
The script can be startet at any time during your run only be carefull with enemies. It will try to kill them in the beginning and if two arrive at the same time they will hit you.
It will get stuck at difficulty 38 if you don't by one armor cheat and then again at 82. There you still can by armor cheates, but it will only increase the difficulty by 2-3 each time. Look at this message in the discord for more information: https://discord.com/channels/488444879836413975/783026949715001364/941159473232371724
You can buy the armor at the beginning of the run.

**This uses `turbo exec v2`, found here: https://github.com/Xenos6666/TPT2_scripts/blob/main/common/turbo_exec/README.md**

Thanks to turbo the script should do all inputs frame perfect. It automatically detects, how fast it can perform any action. So if you find the boots, it will automatically speed up. 
If you find the EOD armor, the purple one, you can press E to enable EOD mode. In this mode it will tank bombs which brings the wait down to 3 frames from 4 move actions. It assumes you found EOD after difficulty 50 (you can find it after 45).
You can set a maximum difficulty it is allowd to clear either by settin it in the `init script` or by adjusting it whith the W (increase) and S (decrease) keys. You can also write you own script to influence this value.
